  "text": "Can you expand on what you meant by the cycling uh instraings of energy? M R there are four types of cycles, which are those given in the moment of entry into incarnation. There are in audition more cosmic and less regularized employments which from time to time affect a sensed mind, body, spirit, complex. The four rhythms are to some extent known among your peoples and are called biorhythms. There is a fourth cycle which we may call the cycle of Gateway of Magic of the Adept or of the Spirit. This is a cycle which is completed in approximately a team of your diurnal cycles. The cosmic patterns are also a function of the moment of incarnative entrance and have to do with your satellite, you call the moon, your planets of this galaxy, the galactic sun, and in some cases of the instreamings from the major galactic points of energy flow.",
